<p>Meanwhile we have started our classes, &amp; notwithstanding a certain number of difficulties in the way of smooth running &amp; good attendance, are progressing. In fact I am fairly certain that if I keep my nose to the wheel, &amp; do not slacken off, there will be quite a good amount of useful work accomplished if we stay here.</p>
